						               													<description>If you too have eaten Casu marzu, if you always carry the Island in your heart, you have chosen the perfect game.&amp;#10;Spuntino is quick and easy, perfect for an evening with friends or family, ideal for adults and children who love good regional cuisine.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With Spuntino's illustrated cards, you can indulge yourself in inventing new culinary combinations and combine a thousand flavors to get more points than your opponents.&amp;#10;Are you ready for an explosion of Sardinian tastes?&amp;#10;Each game lasts about 30 minutes, just like a real snack, and then you'll be ready for a new game where you can enjoy new delightful flavors.&amp;#10;You will have 110 illustrated playing cards at your disposal to create the most combinations and declare a snack. You can also create delicious combinations with wine and &amp;quot;filu'e ferru&amp;quot; and become the sommelier of the family.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The aim of this board game is to get the highest number of points by making combinations of typical Sardinian dishes. To win, you will have to become the Snack King by getting more points than your opponents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
